data.description: Welcome to this stunning countryside retreat on Alum Spring Road! With its newer construction and upgrades, get ready for an unforgettable experience! Step onto the inviting covered front porch and enter into a home adorned with beautiful plank flooring. Discover two owner suites, a cozy family room with a fireplace, and a kitchen boasting granite counters and full-sized fridge and freezer. Upstairs, find more bedrooms and a family room. The fully finished basement with a separate entrance adds even more versatility. Conveniently located near schools and shopping, this home is a must-see! Don't miss the chance to explore this captivating haven and envision the endless possibilities it offers for comfortable living and entertaining. Embrace the serenity of rural life while enjoying modern amenities and easy access to amenities – this is countryside living at its finest! Come and experience the tranquil charm of this extraordinary property firsthand!
